1. *Vise* puta sam zaboravio svoju torbu. (I have forgotten my bag several times.)
2. Njegov tata mu je *vise* puta govorio o tome. (His father has spoken to him about it several times.)
3. Svi smo se *vise* puta slagali. (We have all disagreed multiple times.)
4. Ona se *vise* puta oglasila o tome. (She has spoken out about it several times.)
5. *Vise* od jednom sam je pitao. (I have asked her more than once.)